# ADR Template (Structure)

This is a template layout for ADR orchestration.

```
.adr/
?? README
?? orchestration/
?  ?? <SESSION_NAME>/
?     ?? primary_task_list.md
?     ?? prd.md
?     ?? technical_requirements.md
?     ?? notes.md
?? current/
?  ?? <SESSION_NAME>/
?     ?? phase_1.md
?? history/
   ?? <SESSION_NAME>/
      ?? phase_1.md
      ?? phase_1_review.md
```
